List of top things to keep eye on when writing css

1) Livestyle guide
2) Story book
3) Avoid global and element selectors
   -Oke for sesetting and normalizing
4) Omit overly specific selectors
   -Specifity 
   -Don't chain classes
   -Avoid usign id
5) Use semantic class names ( BEM )
6) Don't tie css to closely to markup structure
7) 



Prefix
.l-layout        ( Layout rules )
.is-state-type   ( State rule )
.js-action-name  ( Non-styled Javascript Hooks )




